- Innocent?

207
00:26:03,415 --> 00:26:04,824
笑死我了
I will give something.

208
00:26:55,326 --> 00:26:58,193
撒哈拉沙漠这么大，他们干嘛非要停在那儿?
The whole damn Sahara and they have to stop here.

209
00:28:25,732 --> 00:28:28,019
- 什么事，军士长
- So, Major?
- 又有车队来了，长官
- More company, sir.

210
00:28:28,191 --> 00:28:29,932
