因此我们要从这儿插过去
guarding Kalafsho Flats while we cut through here.

251
00:33:14,785 --> 00:33:17,189
你知道这条路通到哪儿吗，少校？
Do you realised what you're suggesting, Major?

252
00:33:18,550 --> 00:33:19,592
- 知道,长官
Yes, sir!

253
00:33:19,617 --> 00:33:22,188
- 是德军的雷区！
- That's a German minefield.
- 没错
- That's right.

254
00:33:22,367 --> 00:33:24,441
所以他们不会来这里找我们，他们想不到
Where they're not likely to looks for us.

255
00:33:25,866 --> 00:33:27,707
我不同意,应该掉头
I don't like it. We're turning around.

256
00:33:27,733 --> 00:33:28,723
那么上校，你将会
Do that Colonel and you'll

257
00:33:28,866 --> 00:33:30,773
当一回真正的战俘了
reached Tobruk as a real prisoner.

258
00:33:47,406 --> 00:33:48,815

It's out of the question.

259
00:33:49,072 --> 00:33:51,577
哈克尔上校,你花费尽心思
Colonel Harker you went to an awful lot of trouble to

260
00:33:51,603 --> 00:33:54,049
把我拐进这个行动
shanghai me in on this mission.

261
00:33:54,488 --> 00:33:57,770
可既然你不听愿我的建议，干嘛还非要把我拉来？
If you're not going to follow my advise, what the hell am I doing here?

262
00:33:57,946 --> 00:34:00,777
可没有探雷器,重型车辆根本过不去
You can't take heavy transport through that without mine detector.

263
00:34:00,780 --> 00:34:03,482
你到底要不要听我的？你带我来就要听我的
Why are you telling me? You brought me along to tell you.

264
00:34:04,737 --> 00:34:07,226
好吧,少校，我洗耳恭听
All right... Major, tell me.

265
00:34:09,195 --> 00:34:10,273
谢谢你，长官
Thank you, sir.

266
00:34:13,194 --> 00:34:15,149
把半履带车开过来！
Bring up the half-track.

267
00:34:18,473 --> 00:34:20,772
这个季节刮南风,日复一日
This time of the year, the wind is from the south.

268
00:34:20,943 --> 00:34:23,015
风把沙子长时间吹成这样的斜面
It blows for months at a time forming a

269
00:34:23,041 --> 00:34:25,009
形成厚沙垫能分散压力
sand cushion at the base of the slope.

