You know one wrong tickle with that bayonet

301
00:37:54,892 --> 00:37:56,652
我们就要在坟墓种雏菊了
and we will be pushing up the daisies.

302
00:39:22,285 --> 00:39:25,070
他想一个人挖遍撒哈拉吗?
Does he expect to dig up the whole damn Sahara on his own?

303
00:39:25,827 --> 00:39:27,983
- 军士长泰恩
- Sergeant Major Tyne.
- 长官
- Sir.

304
00:39:29,576 --> 00:39:31,219
叫你的人带上刺刀跟我来
Get some men with bayonets and follow me, will you?

305
00:39:31,221 --> 00:39:31,841
长官
Sir.

306
00:39:49,491 --> 00:39:51,695
你干嘛用手指堵着耳朵？
What have you got your fingers in your ears for?

307
00:39:52,116 --> 00:39:52,779
那你干嘛不用你的爪子
What have you got your 

