Get cracking, there's a schedule to keep.

322
00:42:01,518 --> 00:42:02,560
还好吗？博依德
All right, Boyle?

323
00:42:04,142 --> 00:42:04,865
有什么意见吗？
Any complaints?

324
00:42:04,891 --> 00:42:07,479
给可可多一些糖吗,中士？
How about some more sugar for the cocoa, Sergeant Major?

325
00:42:07,482 --> 00:42:09,640
你有你需要的口粮 
You've had your rations that you need.

